    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="sed"><a href="#sed" class="headerlink" title="sed"></a>sed</h1><h2 id="1-sed删除含有特定字符或字符串的行"><a href="#1-sed删除含有特定字符或字符串的行" class="headerlink" title="1. sed删除含有特定字符或字符串的行"></a>1. sed删除含有特定字符或字符串的行</h2><p><strong>实例:</strong>     </p>
<pre><code>line=$(cat /etc/exports|grep -n /bwfs/fs2|grep -v &apos;#&apos;|awk &apos;BEGIN {FS=&quot;:&quot;} {print $1}&apos;)    
N=$line    
echo &quot;$N&quot;     
if [ &quot;$N&quot; != &quot;0&quot; ];then      
    sed -i &apos;/fs2/d&apos; /etc/exports    
fi    
</code></pre>]]></content>
    
